{"tid":858321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"智力交通題","createTime":"2018-10-11T17:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T23:58:38.000Z","uid":147615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf9e1bb90a8f3c1cc771f9b99d45aa8c1cdd382","tid":858321,"uid":147615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"如果你有1750蚊，由星期一朝早9點開始有3日時間，由北角地鐵站出發搭任何交通工具，最遠可以去到邊呢 ?<br />\n（唔係IQ題，冇標準答案）<br />\n<br />\n1，全部交通工具都要俾錢（唔可以搭Free ride）。<br />\n2，冇長者優惠。<br />\n3，一定要係搭交通工具，唔可以租車自己揸，唔可以租單車，例如過關，轉車轉地鐵站短程可以行。<br />\n4，當唔洗食訓痾既時間同洗費。<br />\n5，所有旅遊證件都跟左身，但未搞任何簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇可能離開到亞洲呢 ? <br />\n請提供任何路線 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5de8c8ae4635c18609bb466cb151082287c4c61","tid":858321,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"樓主要着草<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa2b756193254f579dffa09cc651a222b02c893","tid":858321,"uid":147615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5de8c8ae4635c18609bb466cb151082287c4c61","tid":858321,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"樓主要着草<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}